Pick him up.

30:44.908 --> 30:46.618
Shelly.

30:47.870 --> 30:49.830
I'm going to ask you 10 times.

30:49.913 --> 30:52.374
You understand?

30:52.457 --> 30:53.709
10 times.

31:09.933 --> 31:10.976
One.

31:11.059 --> 31:12.603
Where's our money?

31:12.686 --> 31:13.687
Aah, God!

31:34.541 --> 31:36.169
