from the business.

32:18.210 --> 32:20.546
He came to see me yesterday

32:20.629 --> 32:23.549
because he was afraid
Caesar found out.

32:23.632 --> 32:26.468
He wanted to run, but he
wanted me to come with him.

32:26.552 --> 32:30.180
- Even though he knew about you.
- Yeah.

32:30.264 --> 32:32.641
What, this guy's
in love with you, right?

32:32.724 --> 32:35.853
That's what he tells himself,
but it's not even about me.

32:35.936 --> 32:37.896
You see, he could
have run at any time,

32:37.980 --> 32:39.983
but he didn't want out.

32:40.066 --> 32:41.693
Sounds like he wanted
to get caught.

32:41.776 --> 32:44.279
Yeah. Maybe he did.

32:44.362 --> 32:47.073
He would brag
to me all the time.

32:47.156 --> 32:50.493
