it's over $2 million.

34:01.190 --> 34:03.025
Yeah.

34:03.108 --> 34:04.652
So Caesar's going to get it.

34:04.735 --> 34:06.111
He's going to bring it
by the apartment.

34:06.195 --> 34:07.446
He's going to count it.

34:07.530 --> 34:10.574
He'll go through the books and
figure out how Shelly did it.

34:10.658 --> 34:13.452
Violet, do you know
what you're saying?

34:13.536 --> 34:17.246
