It's kind of like flirting.

35:34.617 --> 35:37.411
It's kind of like foreplay,

35:37.494 --> 35:41.832
because the more they talk
about it, the wetter they get.

35:44.126 --> 35:46.879
The only difference is,
I can fuck someone I just met,

35:48.464 --> 35:49.715
but to steal,

35:49.798 --> 35:52.343
