took us to the money.

36:27.962 --> 36:30.589
I'll tell you something.
Mickey? He knows his shit.

36:30.673 --> 36:32.841
He does. Shelly
took us right there.

36:32.925 --> 36:35.386
So Shelly's down
on his knees, right?

36:35.469 --> 36:37.179
And he's pulling out
this money

36:37.263 --> 36:38.889
from the safe on the floor.

36:38.973 --> 36:40.558
And I'm there,
I'm standing there,

36:40.641 --> 36:43.060
and I'm looking at it, right?

36:43.143 --> 36:45.563
Like, "Holy fuck,"
and all I can think about

36:45.646 --> 36:48.941
is, "How the fuck
was he able to do this?"

36:49.024 --> 36:50.484
When... Bang!

36:50.568 --> 36:52.027
