36:57.032 --> 37:00.161
I have no idea if this
is even all of it.

37:02.080 --> 37:05.458
And right then, I go
through the roof, and... BAM!

37:05.542 --> 37:07.252
I punch the dumb son of a bitch.

37:07.335 --> 37:10.046
I punch him, Vi, right
in his dumb fucking face.

37:10.130 --> 37:11.840
