39:43.910 --> 39:47.205
Yes.

39:48.748 --> 39:50.833
- Tell me about Johnnie.
- Johnnie?

39:50.917 --> 39:52.793
Yeah. Sounds like he and Caesar
don't like each other.

39:52.877 --> 39:54.754
