in his hand.

42:13.644 --> 42:17.105
Unbelievable
what this guy Shelly did.

42:17.189 --> 42:19.858
I'll tell you, Shelly's
one smart-ass motherfucker.

42:19.942 --> 42:23.947
I mean, he WAS one
smart-ass motherfucker.

42:24.030 --> 42:27.742
Poor boy has to work so hard.

42:32.038 --> 42:36.334
