in the apartment.

45:25.753 --> 45:27.839
Everyone's gonna think
I took it.

45:27.922 --> 45:29.299
- Not Caesar.
- Why?

45:29.382 --> 45:31.593
Because of what
you're gonna tell him.

45:31.676 --> 45:33.803
You gotta be
as real as you can.

45:33.888 --> 45:37.683
When you walk through that door
with the Scotch in your hand,

45:37.766 --> 45:39.768
