- Oh, God...
- Caesar?

48:06.499 --> 48:07.500
Cea?

48:09.252 --> 48:11.671
Oh, no. Oh!

48:11.796 --> 48:13.465
Oh, God.

48:17.344 --> 48:19.846
Vi...

48:19.930 --> 48:23.183
