48:38.448 --> 48:42.327
Jesus Christ, Violet,
open your fucking eyes.

48:42.410 --> 48:46.122
Johnnie hates me
as much as I hate him.

48:46.206 --> 48:47.917
I hate that motherless
rat fucker. I hate him.

48:48.000 --> 48:49.835
I fucking hate him. I hate him.

48:49.919 --> 48:53.589
- But you know he did it.
- Yeah, so what?

48:53.673 --> 48:55.883
Violet, so fucking what?

48:55.967 --> 48:59.971
Look, the money is gone, right?

49:00.054 --> 49:01.722
